---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us">
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">About AceServe Solutions</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 text-center">
      At AceServe Solutions, we are dedicated to revolutionizing tennis club management through innovative cloud-based software. Our mission is to empower tennis clubs with tools that streamline operations, enhance member engagement, and promote the growth of the sport.
    </p>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Story</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Founded in 2015 by a team of passionate tennis enthusiasts and technology experts, AceServe Solutions recognized the challenges faced by tennis clubs in managing their day-to-day activities. Combining our love for the game with our expertise in software development, we set out to create a comprehensive solution tailored specifically for tennis clubs.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Our Values</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>Innovation:</strong> Continuously developing cutting-edge solutions to meet the evolving needs of tennis clubs.</li>
        <li><strong>Integrity:</strong> Building trust through transparency, honesty, and ethical practices.</li>
        <li><strong>Collaboration:</strong> Partnering with clubs, coaches, and players to create solutions that truly make a difference.</li>
        <li><strong>Excellence:</strong> Striving for the highest quality in our products and services to ensure customer satisfaction.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Meet Our Team</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        Our diverse team comprises experienced software developers, UX designers, and customer support specialists, all united by a shared passion for tennis and technology. We believe that our collaborative approach and dedication to understanding the unique challenges of tennis clubs set us apart in the industry.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8">
        <!-- Team Member 1 -->
        <div class="card w-60 bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
          <figure class="px-10 pt-10">
            <img src="src/images/jane_doe.jpg" alt="Team Member 1" class="rounded-xl" />
          </figure>
          <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
            <h3 class="card-title">Jane Doe</h3>
            <p>CEO & Co-Founder</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Team Member 2 -->
        <div class="card w-60 bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
          <figure class="px-10 pt-10">
            <img src="src/images/john_smith.jpg" alt="Team Member 2" class="rounded-xl" />
          </figure>
          <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
            <h3 class="card-title">John Smith</h3>
            <p>CTO & Co-Founder</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Add more team members as needed -->
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <section class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">Join Us on Our Journey</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
        We invite you to be part of our journey as we continue to innovate and provide solutions that transform the way tennis clubs operate. Whether you're a club manager, coach, or player, AceServe Solutions is here to serve you.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us</a>
    </section>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
